      "id": "get-asset-by-render-id",
      "name": "Get Asset by Render ID",
      "description": "A render may generate more than one file, such as a video, thumbnail and poster image. When the assets are created the only known id is the render id returned by the original [render request](#render-video), status  request or webhook. This endpoint lets you look up one or more assets by the render id.\n\n**base URL:** https://api.shotstack.io/serve/{version}",
